### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Get all sensors (with real-time values from MQTT)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/sensors

### Get sensor by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/sensors/YOUR_SENSOR_ID_HERE

###
### REGISTER NEW SENSORS
### Note: value and unit are set to 0/empty - they will be updated via MQTT
###

### Register sensor - Must match Pi simulator ID
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sensors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "temp-sensor-01",
  "type": "temperature",
  "location": "Living Room",
  "value": 0,
  "unit": "",
  "status": "active"
}

